# Calculator Microservice

A cloud-native calculator microservice built with Node.js and Express, providing basic arithmetic operations through RESTful endpoints.

## Features

- **Basic Operations**:
  - Addition (`/add`)
  - Subtraction (`/subtract`)
  - Multiplication (`/multiply`)
  - Division (`/divide`)
  - Squareroot (`/divide`)
  - Modulo (`/modulo`)
  - Exponentiation (`/power`)

- **Advanced Features**:
  - Request validation
  - Comprehensive logging
  - Error handling
  - JSON responses with timestamps

## Prerequisites

- Node.js (v14+ recommended)
- npm (comes with Node.js)
- Git (optional)
- Docker
- Minikube
- kubectl
